Add Cmd+Opt+Down/Up shortcuts for sequential tab navigation.

When Browser Layout is set to Vertical and the feature is enabled,
Cmd+Opt+Down/Up navigates to the next/previous tab in strip order.
When conditions are not met, the shortcuts fall through to the
original IDC_FOCUS_NEXT_PANE / IDC_FOCUS_PREVIOUS_PANE behavior.

The setting toggle only appears when Browser Layout = Vertical.
Mac-only shortcuts; Windows/Linux bindings are a follow-up.

